rows.label: fev11_610_150_msg0002
rows.name:
Laura has her award ceremony soon,
right? It's probably not a good idea
to wander off.

rows.label: fev11_610_150_msg0005
rows.name:
I don't mind a walk around the capital,
but we should probably stay on
standby at the inn.

rows.label: fev11_610_150_msg0006
rows.name:
That's a good idea.
We don't know when we'll be contacted.

rows.label: fev11_610_150_msg0007
rows.name:
[ML:Feeling kind=Think ]I guess it's normal,
but everyone's so calm about this.

rows.label: fev11_610_150_msg0008
rows.name:
[ML:Feeling kind=Think ]I have no idea what an award ceremony is
even like, and I'm a nervous wreck...
